3- backup dir url

the new service is integrated with the clean service, when the clean
service attempt to delete a file, it first makes a copy of the file in
the backup dir as .tmp file then the file is renamed to remove the
extension (guaranteeing the backup service exclusive acces to the file

inside which it creates a zip file for the backed up audits.

DCMEEREQ-7 audit record repository with CDI support

1)Provides standard repository as defined by IHE Audit Trail
http://wiki.ihe.net/index.php?title=Audit_Trail_and_Node_Authentication
including:
i-Audit messages following the DICOM XML schema for audit messages
Schema can be found here:
ftp://medical.nema.org/medical/dicom/Trial_Use/sup95_fz.pdf
ii-Provides application activity and audit record used message
generation.
iii-Uses dcm4che implementation for SYSLOG protocol
iv-Supports audit reporting via either TLS or UDP
2)Provides support for LDAP and Java preferences configuration
3)Provides a fully configurable and customizable clean up service for
the audit record repository.
4)provides a restful service for controlling the audit record repository
service as well as querying the repository.
5)Provides a simple web interface for filtering queries
6)Support AuditLogger suppression criteria.

the scheduler threads can delete the empty dir during the naction
response write (before which the files have already been deleted by the

is to check for this case before trying to delete.

commit_list.message:
[#PRX-250 Possible race condition for receiving n-event-rsp]

Solve by copying naction files before actually receiving a valid
response from the destination in both direct and scheduled forwarding.
In case the reponse is success then the naction dir copy is removed
while keeping the copy in the nevent dir, in case of callingAET of the
naction not equal to that of the proxy then the proxy should not receive
nevent reports and therefore the copy in the naction and nevent dirs are
removed, in case of failure the naction file is renamed according to
error and the copy from the nevent dir is removed.
